FT  24 APR 93 / UK Company News: Fitch losses widen to Pounds 3.9m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A SHARP RISE in exceptional provisions left Fitch, a provider of design
services, Pounds 3.98m in the red at the pre-tax level for the year to
end-December, against Pounds 417,000.
